{"id":884,"date":"2017-12-22T04:07:03","date_gmt":"2017-12-22T04:07:03","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/?p=884"},"modified":"2021-02-27T09:47:24","modified_gmt":"2021-02-27T09:47:24","slug":"5-y-tuong-tuyet-voi-giup-ban-gian-lan-dien-tich-nha-nho","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/5-y-tuong-tuyet-voi-giup-ban-gian-lan-dien-tich-nha-nho\/","title":{"rendered":"5 \u00dd t\u01b0\u1edfng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n \u201cgian l\u1eadn\u201d di\u1ec7n t\u00edch nh\u00e0 nh\u1ecf"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">Trong nh\u1ecbp s\u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ee7 nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec7n nghi c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n trong \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n nh\u1ecf, ch\u1eadt h\u1eb9p ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi r\u1ea5t quan t\u00e2m. Nh\u00e0 nh\u1ecf, c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng nh\u1ecf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3&nbsp; r\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ti\u1ec7n \u00edch, \u0111a n\u0103ng, thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n nh\u1edd v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. Nh\u1edd c\u00e1ch trang tr\u00ed \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, c\u00e1ch k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p m\u00e0u s\u1eafc th\u00f4ng minh v\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t c\u00f3 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p, gia \u0111\u00ecnh b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u khi s\u1ed1ng \u1edf kh\u00f4ng gian c\u00f3 di\u1ec7n t\u00edch nh\u1ecf.<\/span><\/p>\n<ol>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>\u01afu ti\u00ean gam m\u00e0u m\u00e0u l\u1ea1nh<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">Nh\u1eefng gam m\u00e0u l\u1ea1nh( \u0111en- tr\u1eafng-x\u00e1m) kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 mang \u0111\u1ebfn n\u00e9t \u0111\u1eb9p c\u00e1 t\u00ednh, n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho m\u1ecdi kh\u00f4ng gian, ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 m\u00e0 c\u00f2n t\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u1ef1c nh\u1edd c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebft ch\u1ebf s\u1eafc \u0111en, x\u00e1m trong kh\u00f4ng gian c\u00f3 n\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf ch\u00fang c\u00f2n linh ho\u1ea1t v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng gian v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed3 n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">Khi\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u1eeba mang v\u1ebb huy\u1ec1n b\u00ed , c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m ph\u1ea7n tinh t\u1ebf, hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i v\u00e0 trang nh\u00e3; mang \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 t\u0129nh l\u1eb7ng v\u00e0 an nhi\u00ean cho m\u1ed7i th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong gia \u0111\u00ecnh b\u1ea1n m\u1ed7i khi v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-889\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/khach-bep-view2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1600\" height=\"950\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/khach-bep-view2.jpg 1600w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/khach-bep-view2-300x178.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/khach-bep-view2-1024x608.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/khach-bep-view2-768x456.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/khach-bep-view2-1536x912.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng gam m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">Trong th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 s\u1ed1, m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua v\u1edbi th\u1eddi gian th\u00ec nh\u1eefng m\u00f3n n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t mang gam m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn con ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n v\u00e0 nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng. M\u00e0u tr\u1eafng tinh kh\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3m b\u1edbt s\u1eafc \u0111\u1ed9 cho c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng nh\u1ecf h\u1eb9p m\u00e0 n\u00f3 c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00ed nh\u01b0 li\u1ec1u thu\u1ed1c gi\u00fap con ng\u01b0\u1eddi xoa d\u1ecbu, x\u00f3a nh\u00f2a m\u1ecdi m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi, \u00e2u lo trong cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-892\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/11-MASTER.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1080\" height=\"810\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/11-MASTER.png 1080w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/11-MASTER-300x225.png 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/11-MASTER-768x576.png 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/11-MASTER-1024x768.png 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">Theo phong th\u1ee7y, m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c d\u01b0\u01a1ng. M\u00e0u tr\u1eafng t\u01b0\u01a1i m\u1edbi t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0ng cho s\u1ef1 tinh khi\u1ebft, th\u1ecbnh v\u01b0\u1ee3ng. M\u00e0u tr\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 m\u00e0u c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1ea1n v\u1eadt, do \u0111\u00f3, m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng c\u00f2n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 h\u1ed3n nhi\u00ean, trong s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3n d\u1ecb. N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 t\u01b0\u01a1i tr\u1ebb, s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng tu\u1ed5i tr\u1ebb, m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n, n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a tr\u00ed tu\u1ec7 v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfp thu t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc trong cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif;\">Ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gian m\u1edf<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t mang phong c\u00e1ch th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i \u201c c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p\u201d r\u1ea5t ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng gian m\u1edf v\u00e0 \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c t\u00f9 t\u00fang, ch\u1eadt h\u1eb9p. Nh\u1eefng khung c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 d\u1ea1ng l\u1edbn, r\u1ed9ng c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao khung c\u1eeda ch\u1ea1m tr\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng di\u1ec7n t\u00edch t\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00ea t\u00f4ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap t\u0103ng s\u1ef1 th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gian c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u1eadp tr\u00e0n \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi. N\u1ebfu c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng qu\u00e1 cao, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng r\u00e8m c\u1eeda 1 l\u1edbp d\u00e0y ho\u1eb7c 2 l\u1edbp m\u1ecfng. Ch\u00fa \u00fd r\u00e8m c\u1eeda n\u00ean c\u00f3 m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng, \u0111en, x\u00e1m,\u2026. \u0110\u1ec3 ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n mang phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, tinh t\u1ebf.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-897\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/5-y-tuong-tuyet-voi-giup-ban-gian-lan-dien-tich-nha-nho-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/5-y-tuong-tuyet-voi-giup-ban-gian-lan-dien-tich-nha-nho-1.jpg 1500w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/5-y-tuong-tuyet-voi-giup-ban-gian-lan-dien-tich-nha-nho-1-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/5-y-tuong-tuyet-voi-giup-ban-gian-lan-dien-tich-nha-nho-1-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/5-y-tuong-tuyet-voi-giup-ban-gian-lan-dien-tich-nha-nho-1-1024x614.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, c\u00e1c gia \u0111\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng x\u00e2y t\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111em l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c ch\u1eadt ch\u1ed9i, r\u1ea5t c\u1ee9ng nh\u1eafc cho ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng linh ho\u1ea1t trong s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng. V\u00e1ch ng\u0103n, v\u00e1ch treo hay b\u00ecnh phong kh\u00f4ng che khu\u1ea5t qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u00ednh ri\u00eang t\u01b0. Khi c\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng gian m\u1edf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 di chuy\u1ec3n ho\u1eb7c th\u00e1o r\u1eddi. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady, v\u00e1ch ng\u0103n hay b\u00ecnh phong c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u h\u1ecda ti\u1ebft hoa v\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c gia \u0111\u00ecnh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn mang l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c s\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft h\u01a1n. Ch\u00fang kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 \u1ea5m \u00e1p, sang tr\u1ecdng cho ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 m\u00e0 c\u00f2n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n ri\u00eang bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a t\u1ed5 \u1ea5m.<\/span><\/p>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng, ti\u1ec7n \u00edch<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">Nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e1 treo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ph\u00f2ng n\u00e0o trong nh\u00e0. Ch\u00fang kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y t\u1ed1n di\u1ec7n t\u00edch m\u00e0 c\u00f2n t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh n\u01a1i l\u01b0u \u0111\u1ed3 m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng l\u00e0m k\u1ec7 trang tr\u00ed trang t\u00ednh th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o cho n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t nh\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p ri\u00eang, \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1eeb c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-886\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Ban-biet-gi-ve-phong-cach-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-4-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"5472\" height=\"3648\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Ban-biet-gi-ve-phong-cach-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-4-1.jpg 5472w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Ban-biet-gi-ve-phong-cach-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-4-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Ban-biet-gi-ve-phong-cach-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-4-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Ban-biet-gi-ve-phong-cach-thiet-ke-noi-that-hien-dai-4-1-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 5472px) 100vw, 5472px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">C\u00e1c g\u00f3c t\u01b0\u1eddng lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed kh\u00f3&nbsp; \u0111\u1ec3 trang tr\u00ed v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ecb l\u00e3ng qu\u00ean m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch l\u00e3ng ph\u00ed. B\u1ea1n h\u00e3y s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o g\u00f3c t\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1ed1ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean h\u1eefu \u00edch v\u00e0 trang \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00eam cho ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 b\u1ea1n<\/span><\/p>\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>Thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd v\u1edbi chi\u1ec1u cao<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">&nbsp;Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea1n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng di\u1ec7n t\u00edch cho c\u0103n h\u1ed9 nh\u1ecf b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a chi\u1ec1u cao. Mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea1o \u1ea3o gi\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chi\u1ec1u cao c\u1ee7a c\u0103n h\u1ed9, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng k\u1ec7 nh\u1ecf m\u1edf cao v\u1edbi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf thanh m\u1ea3nh thu h\u00fat \u00e1nh nh\u00ecn l\u00ean tr\u00ean. Nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea1n n\u00ean l\u01b0u \u00fd kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean \u201c nh\u1ed3i nh\u00e9t\u201d qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ea1c l\u00ean k\u1ec7, nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3n t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n b\u1eeba b\u1ed9n v\u00e0 r\u1ed1i m\u1eaft.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-898\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/48.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"804\" height=\"442\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/48.png 804w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/48-300x165.png 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-co